WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.533 --> 00:00:04.466
Li Feiyu, what do you want to say?

2
00:00:09.366 --> 00:00:11.633
Is Guo Meichen important?

3
00:00:11.866 --> 00:00:13.800
Put down the gun and don't go off

4
00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:15.366
People will die

5
00:00:15.366 --> 00:00:16.433
Mr. Lin

6
00:00:16.500 --> 00:00:18.600
You don't want to see this son-in-law you chose

7
00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:20.033
Who will she choose?

8
00:00:23.266 --> 00:00:26.433
Beichen, what are you looking at me for?

9
00:00:26.466 --> 00:00:27.600
Don't you forget

10
00:00:27.733 --> 00:00:30.633
I'm pregnant with your flesh and blood in my belly

11
00:00:33.933 --> 00:00:36.500
Beichen, I am willing to take this shot for you

12
00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:39.800
Dear, don't be stupid.

13
00:00:40.466 --> 00:00:42.300
Bullets don't have eyes

14
00:00:42.366 --> 00:00:44.700
That's life-threatening.

15
00:00:45.133 --> 00:00:45.900
Beichen

16
00:00:45.900 --> 00:00:48.400
Are you really doing this for the sake of your society?

17
00:00:48.400 --> 00:00:51.300
Do you want to kill your wife?

18
00:00:51.900 --> 00:00:54.100
My father once taught me

19
00:00:54.166 --> 00:00:55.166
Share your worries for your husband

20
00:00:55.400 --> 00:00:56.633
It's my job.

21
00:00:57.533 --> 00:00:59.833
If Beichen insists on letting me fire this shot

22
00:01:00.066 --> 00:01:01.200
I will never run away

23
00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:02.100
Brother Gu

24
00:01:02.733 --> 00:01:04.200
You were a soldier too, right?

25
00:01:04.366 --> 00:01:06.000
Did the bullet in this gun escape?

26
00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:07.366
You should know it yourself.

27
00:01:07.366 --> 00:01:09.666
River, you shouldn't have fired this shot

28
00:01:10.133 --> 00:01:11.033
Right, bear?

29
00:01:12.533 --> 00:01:15.300
Qin Jiang, I know you are playing with me

30
00:01:15.566 --> 00:01:16.666
Let go of my hand

31
00:01:16.800 --> 00:01:19.833
So I'll give you another bet.

32
00:01:19.900 --> 00:01:21.466
If you win

33
00:01:21.933 --> 00:01:24.200
You don't need to pay back the previous money and favors.

34
00:01:24.766 --> 00:01:27.366
And I'm going to use all my relationships.

35
00:01:27.366 --> 00:01:28.800
Secure your Fucheng Reset home

36
00:01:28.933 --> 00:01:30.100
What do you think?

37
00:01:36.133 --> 00:01:38.300
Guangqiang, get out of here

38
00:01:38.300 --> 00:01:40.233
Put the gun down!

39
00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:41.200
Dad

40
00:01:41.966 --> 00:01:43.266
Don't worry about me

41
00:01:43.766 --> 00:01:45.433
You forget how you taught me

42
00:01:48.866 --> 00:01:50.700
I was born a family man

43
00:01:51.300 --> 00:01:52.633
Death is the ghost of the Gu family

44
00:01:53.200 --> 00:01:54.666
As the wife of Beichen

45
00:01:54.666 --> 00:01:56.966
It is my duty to share my husband's worries

46
00:01:56.966 --> 00:01:58.666
Even at the cost of my life

47
00:01:58.766 --> 00:02:00.833
No matter when and where

48
00:02:01.533 --> 00:02:03.966
I have to believe in my husband with all my heart

49
00:02:05.300 --> 00:02:06.166
You say yes

50
00:02:07.066 --> 00:02:09.100
Father

51
00:02:10.866 --> 00:02:13.800
Beichen, I believe you dare to rob it?

